---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - RoyalPrompt" description="Cookie Policy for RoyalPrompt website - Learn about how we use cookies and similar technologies.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        This Cookie Policy explains how RoyalPrompt ("we", "our", or "us") uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit our website at royalprompt.app (the "Website").
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and to provide information to website owners.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Cookies can be "persistent" (remaining on your device until deleted or expired) or "session" cookies (deleted when you close your browser).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable basic functions like page navigation, access to secure areas, and form submissions. The website cannot function properly without these cookies.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Session Management:</strong> To maintain your session while browsing our website</li>
        <li><strong>Security:</strong> To protect against cross-site request forgery (CSRF) attacks</li>
        <li><strong>Form Data:</strong> To temporarily store form data to prevent loss if you navigate away</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.2 Analytics Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting and reporting information anonymously. This helps us improve our website's performance and user experience.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> To track website usage, page views, and user behavior</li>
        <li><strong>Performance Monitoring:</strong> To identify slow-loading pages and technical issues</li>
        <li><strong>User Journey:</strong> To understand how users navigate through our website</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.3 Functional Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        These cookies enable enhanced functionality and personalization, such as remembering your preferences and choices.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Language Preferences:</strong> To remember your preferred language</li>
        <li><strong>Theme Settings:</strong> To remember your display preferences (dark/light mode)</li>
        <li><strong>Form Preferences:</strong> To remember your contact form preferences</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may use third-party services that set their own cookies. These include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics and performance monitoring</li>
        <li><strong>Social Media Platforms:</strong> If you interact with social media buttons or widgets</li>
        <li><strong>Content Delivery Networks:</strong> To optimize website loading speed</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        These third parties have their own privacy policies and cookie practices. We recommend reviewing their policies for more information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookie Duration</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Different cookies have different lifespans:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
        <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain on your device for a set period (typically 30 days to 2 years)</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Usually expire after 2 years</li>
        <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> Typically expire after 1 year</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        You have several options for managing cookies:
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.1 Browser Settings</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. You can:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Block all cookies</li>
        <li>Block third-party cookies only</li>
        <li>Delete existing cookies</li>
        <li>Set your browser to notify you when cookies are set</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.2 Cookie Consent</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        When you first visit our website, you may see a cookie consent banner. You can:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Accept all cookies</li>
        <li>Reject non-essential cookies</li>
        <li>Customize your cookie preferences</li>
        <li>Change your preferences at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.3 Opt-Out Links</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        For specific third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-royal-600 hover:text-royal-700 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google Ads:</strong> <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" class="text-royal-600 hover:text-royal-700 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        If you choose to disable cookies, some features of our website may not function properly:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Contact forms may not work correctly</li>
        <li>Your preferences may not be saved</li>
        <li>Some interactive features may be unavailable</li>
        <li>Website performance may be affected</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Mobile App vs Website</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        This Cookie Policy applies only to our website. Our mobile application (RoyalPrompt app) does not use traditional web cookies but may use similar technologies for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Device identification and analytics</li>
        <li>App performance monitoring</li>
        <li>User preference storage</li>
        <li>Offline functionality</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        For information about data collection in our mobile app, please refer to our <a href="/privacy" class="text-royal-600 hover:text-royal-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on this page.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@royalprompt.app<br>
          <strong>Subject:</strong> Cookie Policy Inquiry<br>
          <strong>Address:</strong> RoyalPrompt Privacy Team<br>
          [Your Company Address]
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
